other_tests.findings: Unremarkable liver except for diffuse mild hepatic steatosis with 9% fat fraction, small 1 cm cyst; minimal intrahepatic and extra biliary ductal dilatation without findings of stricture or focal lesion; gallbladder contains sludge; unremarkable pancreas, spleen, and adrenal glands except for right adrenal adenoma; no hydronephrosis, a few simple renal cysts; incidental juxtapapillary duodenal diverticulum; small to moderate hiatal hernia; no bowel obstruction; no lymphadenopathy in the upper abdomen; patent hepatic vasculature; no suspicious osseous lesion.
